NOTES:
Right this is a re-encode of coalitions release....which isn't too bad at all.
The video they used was pleaders which has been out for some time but never used due to a lack of
some decent audio.The video quality is not to bad,is on the dull side and lacks colour....also is heavily cropped
at the bottom and not the sharpest they done.
Audio pretty good by todays standards......so well done.

WORK DONE:
The main thing was to brighten this up and give it some colour.......so there was a big increase in the chroma,gamma
and lum....also then needed to equal it out with the contrast and make the black look more like black instead of grey.
After doing the but i then needed to lower the rgb black base to remove the bright parts .
Finally i used a contour and a video noise reduction filter......used the contour on a very high setting to try and help sharpen it
up a touch and the video noise reduction was just used slightly.

Overall 7.5 all round IMO
